### **4. 32_RealtimeChartScope**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes numeric streams on a live, scrolling line chart using Matplotlib.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# RealtimeChartScope - Live Data Stream Visualizer

RealtimeChartScope takes incoming numeric values and turns them into dynamic, animated charts.

## Features
- Smooth chart animations  
- Adjustable refresh intervals  
- CLI-friendly  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/32_RealtimeChartScope.git
cd 32_RealtimeChartScope
python visualize.py
